HEADWORD: Recalcitrant
<hw>Re*cal"ci*trant</hw> <pr>(r⟦esl⟧*k⟦acr⟧l"s⟦icr⟧*tr⟦ait⟧nt)</pr>,
<pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L. <ets>recalcitrans</ets>, p. pr. of
